Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.69,0:00:28.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最終的舞臺在呼喚我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.00,0:00:10.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-----------------新OP-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.19,0:00:37.75,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絶望的に君はきれいさ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.90,0:00:44.95,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反転する世界のプラトニック 愛し合おう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.19,0:01:00.60,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僕らが見てる世界は いつでも逆さまで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.42,0:01:11.07,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,どうしようもないことで たいがい決まってく
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.47,0:01:23.15,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涙するほど傷つく瞳 心で叫びながら黙っていた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.39,0:01:33.74,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後のふたり 混ざれないまま 秒読みが聞こえてくる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.54,0:01:39.90,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絶望的に君はきれいさ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.16,0:01:45.75,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,すたれゆく動物みたいに愛し合おう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.81,0:01:50.12,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泣きたいくらい君はきれいさ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.26,0:01:53.46,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反転する世界のプラトニック
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.58,0:01:56.47,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感じたいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.19,0:00:37.75,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你美得令人絕望
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.90,0:00:44.95,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們在倒錯的精神世界中相愛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.19,0:01:00.60,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們眼裡的世界總是相互顛倒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.42,0:01:11.07,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這幾乎要被認定為是無可奈何的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.47,0:01:23.15,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傷口淌淚的眼眸 在內心沉默地叫喊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.39,0:01:33.74,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後的兩人來不及結合便聽到離別的倒數
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.54,0:01:39.90,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你美得令人絕望
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.16,0:01:45.75,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們像漸趨衰老的動物一樣相愛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.81,0:01:50.12,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你美得令人落淚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.26,0:01:53.46,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在倒錯的精神世界裡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.58,0:01:56.47,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想細細體會…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,==================OP=================
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.36,0:02:08.90,biaoti,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(719,400)}復活之翼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.67,0:02:15.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這音色 這旋律
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.55,0:02:17.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太適合於最終樂章了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.47,0:02:22.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼續吧 繼續奏響吧 Aquarion
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.95,0:02:23.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修雷特
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.15,0:02:27.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的身體哪裡還藏有如此強大的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.32,0:02:28.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.36,0:02:29.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優雅而纖細
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.92,0:02:31.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但又灼熱而激烈
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.40,0:02:34.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,氣勢雄渾地響徹心底
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.78,0:02:37.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這還是第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.11,0:02:41.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修雷特在不穿Element制服的情況下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.56,0:02:43.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通過強行露出自己的肌膚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.57,0:02:45.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使自己的感官得到進一步的加強
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.85,0:02:49.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但肉體所受的打擊應該相當巨大
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.75,0:02:51.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那簡直就是捨身戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.25,0:02:54.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修雷特
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.54,0:02:59.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為我的靈魂奉上最精彩的獨奏協奏曲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.54,0:02:59.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(577,440)\fs24}Kadenz
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.45,0:03:07.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時候我所看到的不是幻覺
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.97,0:03:09.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.19,0:03:14.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難怪第一次相遇時沒有聞到你的氣味
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.91,0:03:18.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你和我有著相同的氣味
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.38,0:03:21.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這張照片裡的人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.62,0:03:22.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.21,0:03:24.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同時也是你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.95,0:03:29.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和我原本是一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.39,0:03:32.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 直到那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.61,0:03:35.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.95,0:03:38.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.59,0:03:40.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要走
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.75,0:04:04.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一天 那個只能任由命運擺佈的阿馬塔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.57,0:04:07.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.19,0:04:13.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到現在你也沒什麼改變
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.75,0:04:17.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是那個一到關鍵時刻就束手無策的膽小鬼阿馬塔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.23,0:04:19.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又有什麼了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.01,0:04:22.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到最後都救不了媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.12,0:04:25.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去Altair都做些什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.44,0:04:32.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然穿越了次元 但我和母親失散了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.25,0:04:35.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這時候我遇到了未影
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.40,0:04:39.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎 半身的你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.07,0:04:41.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暗之阿馬塔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.51,0:04:49.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫做神樂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.55,0:04:52.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從今天起你就叫神樂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.79,0:04:58.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我失去了記憶 由未影一手撫養
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.54,0:05:04.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今 母親的事已經無所謂了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.75,0:05:08.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就跟連不明來歷的父親也一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.45,0:05:11.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我來說重要的氣味是唯一的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.99,0:05:15.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就只有心愛的臭女人的氣味
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.91,0:05:18.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的希爾菲而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.05,0:05:21.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是膽小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.57,0:05:25.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會把御子乃交給你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.14,0:05:32.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真弱真弱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.71,0:05:35.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太弱了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.85,0:05:39.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 為什麼你們兩人要戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.28,0:05:42.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了 快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.15,0:05:47.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太陽之翼終於覺醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.11,0:06:25.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 阿馬塔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.92,0:06:28.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我看看你是怎麼地不軟弱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.88,0:06:37.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.53,0:06:46.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御子乃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.61,0:06:47.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希爾菲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.19,0:06:53.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御子乃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.50,0:07:04.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然是Aquarion
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.93,0:07:12.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.03,0:07:14.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高次元量子反應
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.73,0:07:16.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在湖泊一帶的地底下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.25,0:07:33.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個標誌是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.83,0:07:36.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Aquarion居然產生了共鳴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.45,0:07:41.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是從1萬2千年前的太古傳來的旋律
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.38,0:07:44.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會錯的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.10,0:07:49.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那正是傳說中的神話型Aquarion
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.01,0:08:05.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太陽之翼終於現身了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.42,0:08:16.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.31,0:08:20.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Aquarion
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.03,0:08:22.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 那是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.35,0:08:24.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御子乃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.87,0:08:26.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御子乃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.46,0:08:27.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿馬塔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.08,0:08:29.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希爾菲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.08,0:08:33.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好想你啊 希爾菲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.68,0:08:35.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跨越了1萬2千年的時空
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.10,0:08:39.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在終於能夠殺死你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.29,0:08:40.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要殺掉御子乃?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.15,0:08:43.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 我要殺掉她
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.19,0:08:49.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛苦地 激烈地 冷酷地 無數次地殺死她
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.31,0:08:53.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但在那之前
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.22,0:08:57.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要殺掉你 阿馬塔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.70,0:08:59.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等著我 希爾菲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.53,0:09:03.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹掉他之後 讓我們好好地廝殺至天明
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.47,0:09:04.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.83,0:09:07.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會讓你碰她一根指頭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.56,0:09:24.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高次元量子等級正持續上升
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.78,0:09:28.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會錯的 這是真傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.30,0:09:31.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神話型Aquarion
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.95,0:09:34.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傳說終於化為現實
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.58,0:09:38.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們正身處在如此偉大的歷史瞬間面前嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.15,0:09:41.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 明明到了這麼重要的時刻
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.37,0:09:44.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙到底在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.14,0:09:48.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也是傳說之一
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.76,0:09:51.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不動總司令 您什麼時候回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.84,0:09:57.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打情罵俏 犬亦不理
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.95,0:10:03.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿馬塔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.44,0:10:15.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕不交給你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.44,0:10:20.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放棄吧 這是1萬2千年前就已經決定好的命運
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.31,0:10:23.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和希爾菲結合的不是你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.56,0:10:27.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論你怎麼掙扎也無法戰勝命運
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.38,0:10:31.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和希爾菲正因是被命運所指引著
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.05,0:10:34.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以即使身處不同的星球也能相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.18,0:10:37.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有著能跨越命運的翅膀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.99,0:10:43.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算有翅膀 不用以飛翔也是毫無意義的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.78,0:10:44.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能飛起來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.06,0:10:46.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 飛起來給我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.80,0:10:53.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 你不可以繼續傷害阿馬塔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.78,0:10:55.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的笑臉太難看了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.43,0:10:58.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我越來越想殺死你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.81,0:11:01.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑吧 繼續笑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.74,0:11:04.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼續吧 繼續吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.77,0:11:20.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.94,0:11:25.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經死了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.87,0:11:28.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿馬塔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.31,0:11:32.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 你沒事啊 婕希卡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.57,0:11:37.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿馬塔才是 難道說你是擔心我才回來…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.63,0:11:43.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,婕希卡 我終於意識到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.13,0:11:46.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正重要的到底是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.07,0:11:47.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿馬塔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.64,0:11:52.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 快醒醒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.69,0:11:57.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還不能死
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.21,0:11:59.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.37,0:12:06.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和我的約定還沒有兌現
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.71,0:12:13.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.61,0:12:20.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還不能死
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.07,0:12:25.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為 你和我的約定還沒有兌現
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.88,0:12:31.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約定
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.29,0:12:37.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你了 快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.85,0:12:41.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想再看到你們兩人互相傷害
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.47,0:12:42.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 御子乃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.08,0:12:45.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天一定要做個了斷
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.77,0:12:48.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要了斷什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.17,0:12:53.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是因為命運才追求御子乃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.63,0:12:56.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 不要讓我一再說明
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.78,0:12:59.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.72,0:13:02.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管御子乃是不是希爾菲轉世
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.86,0:13:06.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和1萬2千年前的命運也沒有關係
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.70,0:13:10.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對現在的…現在的御子乃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.22,0:13:12.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿馬塔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.92,0:13:14.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿馬塔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.42,0:13:20.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在 此時此刻 這一瞬間的 御子乃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.38,0:13:23.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就在這裡較量一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.79,0:13:27.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的命運和你的癡情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.56,0:13:29.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪個更加強烈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.89,0:13:40.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿馬塔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.03,0:13:47.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.12,0:13:51.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太陽之翼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.10,0:14:02.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會輸個你這種人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.94,0:14:11.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還差一點 還差一點我所追求的旋律就…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.63,0:14:15.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修雷特
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.63,0:14:16.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修雷特
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.72,0:14:19.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你怎麼了 修雷特
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.03,0:14:22.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽得到嗎 摯友
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.93,0:14:24.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這音色很美妙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.78,0:14:37.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希爾菲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.70,0:14:38.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御子乃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.76,0:14:46.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修雷特的生命等級異常低下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.23,0:14:49.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼續進行戰鬥會危及性命
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.06,0:14:51.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更換Element
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.62,0:14:53.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由柚葉替換修雷特
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.04,0:14:54.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.08,0:14:59.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還能戰鬥 還差一步
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.44,0:15:02.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還差一步 我就…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.32,0:15:05.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更換Element 快
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.71,0:15:10.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚葉·蘇爾 參戰
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.35,0:15:21.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡逃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.03,0:15:30.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神話型Aquarion的高次元量子反應已經超出了檢測範圍
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.27,0:15:35.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不動 你到底想要做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.49,0:15:39.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切不都已經顯示在創聖之書上了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.54,0:15:43.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神話只能由高尚的生命撰寫
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.03,0:15:48.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 以流蕩著的血液為墨
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.78,0:15:51.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒有阻止的意思呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.90,0:15:54.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阻止還是慫恿都是一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.57,0:16:00.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合十的雙手之間到底有什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.85,0:16:03.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其中什麼也沒有 只有無
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.87,0:16:09.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 無雖無 但又不盡為無
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.61,0:16:14.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正負的兩種力量相互抵消產生出無的形態
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.30,0:16:19.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御子乃·鈴白的連接之力亦然
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.55,0:16:28.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光與暗 聖與邪 善與惡 還有陰與陽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.42,0:16:32.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩人封閉著的記憶被打開
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.52,0:16:36.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從虛無中誕生的無限力量開始運動
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.04,0:16:41.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是現在新的一頁即將翻開
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.96,0:17:16.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.95,0:17:24.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.50,0:17:35.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太陽之翼在我的懷抱中
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.10,0:17:43.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神話型Aquarion
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.69,0:17:49.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿馬塔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.88,0:17:53.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,門打開了 我們也快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.58,0:18:13.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2台Abductor以及神話型Aquarion沖入了次元之門中
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.82,0:18:19.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了 克蕾亞理事長
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.03,0:18:23.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請再一次 再一次讓我去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.81,0:18:29.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次真的會沒命哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.45,0:18:38.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被你收留的我來到Neo DEAVA時就已經明白
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.36,0:18:41.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一天遲早會到來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.68,0:19:03.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請答應我一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.05,0:19:08.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曲子完成以後也讓我聽一聽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.17,0:19:18.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御子乃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.81,0:19:22.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修雷特
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.78,0:19:27.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2台Vector闖入次元之門
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.09,0:19:29.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,監視器畫面被中斷
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.17,0:19:37.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御子乃和神樂呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.98,0:19:38.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿馬塔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.68,0:19:46.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在奏響最後的樂曲之前
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.73,0:19:50.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先奪回神話型Aquarion
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.01,0:19:52.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是只有兩人的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.74,0:19:54.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來跟你們合體
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.78,0:19:56.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,婕希卡 你沒事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.99,0:20:01.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿馬塔 這就是我的愛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.53,0:20:06.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命運合體 GO Aquarion
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.28,0:20:16.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿馬塔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.93,0:20:18.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你 婕希卡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.18,0:20:22.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靈魂在顫動
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.75,0:20:29.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Aquarion SPADA
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.83,0:20:35.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神話型被…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.59,0:20:40.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上鉤了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.43,0:20:46.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.59,0:20:50.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 接招吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.88,0:20:53.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,磔刑斬擊劍
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.88,0:20:53.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\pos(424,439)}CRUCIFXION SWORD
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.37,0:21:13.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修雷特
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.46,0:21:20.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次元之門開啟
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.98,0:21:23.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mithra Gnis入侵我領域
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.79,0:21:25.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機體中有Rare·Igler反應
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.34,0:21:29.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓神樂如此執著的Rare·Igler
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.90,0:21:33.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次的一定是真實的夏娃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.91,0:21:36.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.19,0:21:41.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能讓神樂獨佔真實的夏娃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.69,0:21:51.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從世界各地傳來地殼變動和氣候異常的報告
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.76,0:21:55.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由於解除了神話型Aquarion的封印
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.95,0:22:00.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Altair和Vega之間保持至今的平衡已經被打破
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.95,0:22:02.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神話型Aquarion被奪走
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.24,0:22:05.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和修雷特他們的通信也依然斷絕著
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.27,0:22:09.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們這邊就沒有什麼辦法嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.91,0:22:12.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界將會怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.76,0:22:14.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在放棄還太早
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.53,0:22:21.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太陽之翼只有被選中的Element才能操縱
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.69,0:22:27.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時機終於來臨了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.13,0:22:33.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到你履行約定的時候了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.56,0:22:37.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,草綠色頭髮的你
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.36,0:24:24.78,biaoti,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,0)\pos(271,400)}神話旋律
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.00,0:24:13.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我告訴你我喜歡的東西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.97,0:24:15.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,點點的花瓣
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.62,0:24:17.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神樂的咆哮
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.73,0:24:19.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭的東西也告訴你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.22,0:24:25.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是欺騙 背叛 和那個男人
